'''''Yammka's Mount''''' was the [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] of [[Warmaster]] [[Nas Choka]] during the final days of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The warship first saw action during the [[Defense of Mon Calamari (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Defense of Mon Calamari]], when the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] launched a massive attack on the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] capital. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], ''Yammka's Mount'' lost six of its eight primary [[dovin basal]]s, as well as a great deal of its [[Yaret-Kor|lava cannons]], but the vessel ultimately survived the battle.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

